illes and Peacemaking\n  |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/worldwars/wwone/versailles_01.shtml  |accessdate= 30 August 2018\n  |publisher= [[BBC|www.bbc.co.uk]]  |ref= harv}}\n:{{cite encyclopedia |last= Herbst |first= Stanis\u0142aw \n|title= Tadeusz Ko\u015bciuszko |work= Polski S\u0142ownik Biograficzny, 439 pages |volume= 14 |year= 1969 \n|location= Warszawa|publisher= Instytut Historii (Polska Akademia Nauk)|language= Polish\n|ref= harv}}\n:{{cite news\n  |last= Holdsworth  |first= Nick  |date= 18 October 2008\n  |title= Stalin 'planned to send a million troops to stop Hitler if Britain and France agreed pact'&#8239;\n  |url= https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/russia/3223834/Stalin-planned-to-send-a-million-troops-to-stop-Hitler-if-Britain-and-France-agreed-pact.html  |accessdate= 20 October 2013\n  |newspaper= [[The Daily Telegraph|telegraph.co.uk]]  |ref= harv}}\n:{{Cite magazine\n  |author= J.P.  |date= 31 July 2010\n  |title= The Warsaw Rising: Was it all worth it?\n  |url= https://www.economist.com/blogs/easternapproaches/2010/07/warsaw_rising  |accessdate= 20 October 2013\n  |work= Eastern approaches  |publisher= [[The Economist|economist.com]]\n  |ref= harv}}\n:{{Citation\n  |first=W\u0142odzimierz\n  |last=Kalicki\n  |date=23 August 2009\n  |url=http://wyborcza.pl/1,101285,6952313,Norman_Davies__W_1939_r__Polacy_sie_swietnie_spisali.html\n  |title=Norman Davies: W 1939 r. Polacy si\u0119 \u015bwietnie spisali\n  |trans-title=Norman Davies: In 1939, the Poles performed exceedingly well\n  |publisher=[[Gazeta Wyborcza|wyborcza.pl]]\n  |accessdate=29 October 2015\n  |author-link=W\u0142odzimierz Kalicki\n  |ref= {{Harvid|Kalicki|2009}}}}\n:{{Cite book\n  |last= Kemp-Welch  |first= A.  |year= 2008\n  |title= Poland under Communism: A Cold War History\n  |location= Cambridge  |publisher= [[Cambridge University Press]]\n  |isbn= 978-0-521-71117-3  |ref= harv}}\n:{{Cite book\n  |last= Kirchmayer  |first= Jerzy  |authorlink= Jerzy Kirchmayer  |y