ation with German historian Jochen B\u00f6hler)\n  |publisher=[[Gazeta Wyborcza|wyborcza.pl]]\n  |accessdate=30 October 2015\n  |ref= {{Harvid|Wieli\u0144ski|2011}}}}\n:{{Cite book  |last= Williams  |first= Brian Glyn  |authorlink= Brian Glyn Williams  |year= 2013  |title= The Sultan's Raiders: The Military Role of the Crimean Tatars in the Ottoman Empire  |url= http://www.jamestown.org/uploads/media/Crimean_Tatar_-_complete_report_01.pdf  |accessdate= 21 October 2013  |location= Washington, D.C.  |publisher= [[The Jamestown Foundation]]  |ref= harv  |url-status= dead  |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131021092115/http://www.jamestown.org/uploads/media/Crimean_Tatar_-_complete_report_01.pdf  |archivedate= 21 October 2013  }}\n:{{Citation\n  |last=Wodecka\n  |first=Dorota\n  |date=8 November 2013\n  |url=http://wyborcza.pl/magazyn/1,134728,14919359,Polska_urojona.html\n  |title=Polska urojona\n  |trans-title=Imaginary Poland (a conversation with Jan Sowa)\n  |publisher=[[Gazeta Wyborcza|wyborcza.pl]]\n  |accessdate=31 October 2015\n  |ref= {{Harvid|Wodecka|2013}}}}\n:{{Citation\n  |last=Wo\u0142k-\u0141aniewska\n  |first=Agnieszka\n  |date=20 January 2018\n  |url=http://strajk.eu/mamy-przechlapane-rozmowa-z-prof-karolem-modzelewskim/\n  |title=Mamy przechlapane. Rozmowa z prof. Karolem Modzelewskim\n  |trans-title=We've got it all screwed up. A conversation with Prof. Karol Modzelewski\n  |publisher=Strajk.eu\n  |accessdate=2 February 2018\n  |ref= {{Harvid|Wo\u0142k-\u0141aniewska|2018}}}}\n:{{Citation\n  |last=Wro\u0144ski\n  |first=Pawe\u0142\n  |date=1 March 2013\n  |url=http://bialystok.gazeta.pl/bialystok/1,35235,13483112,Dzien_Zolnierzy_Wykletych__Cywilny_opor_czy_III_wojna_.html\n  |title=Dzie\u0144 \u017bo\u0142nierzy Wykl\u0119tych. Cywilny op\u00f3r czy III wojna? Rozmowa z dr hab. Rafa\u0142em Wnukiem\n  |trans-title=The day of cursed soldiers. Civil resistance or World War III? A conversation with Professor Rafa\u0142 Wnuk\n  |publisher=[[Gazet